Heres how it works.

Heres how it works.

Understand the voice of your customer and get to the why fast. Get rich insights in real time.

Understand the voice of your customer and get to the why fast. Get rich insights in real time.

Design.

Give your AI interviewer an objective, some questions, and a brief with additional useful context, just as you would with a human researcher.

Share.

Send the interview link to your customers, or let us find participants for you we integrate with panel providers globally.

Interview.

Tellets AI is conducting interviews, in over 50 languages, with dynamic follow-up questions. Your participants respond with voice notes full of detail.

Analyse.

Tellets AI does the heavy lifting in seconds, giving you key themes, emerging patterns, opportunities and recommendations. Got a hunch? Ask your transcripts new questions whenever you like using AI Search.
